# Upload & import rules

## Classic flow (unchanged behavior)

`Operations/Uploads/Create` → `Details` (per `ReportType` file) → `Map` → Validate → `RunImportAsync`.

Minimum package warning: Sales + Inventory + AR + AP (`RequiredFields.MinimumPackageForV1`).

## Simplified flow

- `UploadBatch.ImportMode = Simplified`, `Cadence`, `AnchorPeriodEnd`
- Pages: `Operations/Uploads/Simplified/Detect`, `Verify`
- `WorkbookAnalyzer` + `SheetClassifier` + `ColumnSynonymMatcher` + `PeriodExtractor`
- Multi-week: loop `FilteredPeriodEnds` ≥ anchor; scoring via `IWeeklyScoringService`
- Rollup sheet KPI mapping: `Gross_Margin_%` → `GrossMargin%`; `AR_Over_60_%` → `AR_PastDue31p%` (approximation — document warning)

## Excel

- **ExcelDataReader** in Web + Infrastructure (not ClosedXML).
- Steve reference fixture: `tests/DecisionOS.Distribution.Tests/Fixtures/Steves_Bowling_Supply_DPOS_Distribution_Test_Data.xlsx`

## Tests to run after import changes

```bash
dotnet test tests/DecisionOS.Distribution.Tests --filter "UploadBatch|Simplified|Workbook"
```

Optional Postgres E2E: `Postgres_SimplifiedImportTests` (needs local DB + fixture).
